snippet.title: Sonic Riders X: Planet Wisp
snippet.description:
Custom Stage for Sonic Riders X based off of Planet Wisp from Sonic Colors.
Check out the new version: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1DpYypB1uAQ
Music: Planet Wisp (Act 1)

The Download is the new version of the stage
Download: https://www.dropbox.com/scl/fi/t5zxatg6zxunle6ym9zsy/customstage?rlkey=p5eoh1q9cwdi4bgn5ldwjhfdd&dl=0

Sonic Riders X by "Giygas" and the dev team
https://discord.gg/zfKBksRUtH

Check out my other stuff here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LNndGunk4CA&list=PLZ-3heNr31hkFuxtTA5-Uh_CDj5FSRa3_
Note that this video is outdated, the stage looks much nicer than the video suggests. Maybe I will create another video showcasing the final update

#SonicFanGames #SonicRidersX
